{
  "texts": [
    "Evaluation will be conducted at pre-intervention (T1), post-intervention (T2), and 3 months follow-up after intervention completion (T3).",
    "The target population will be Hong Kong community-dwelling older adults.",
    "Participants will be recruited and randomly assigned into one of three groups.",
    "The intervention givers (i.e., PA coach and nutritionist) will be blinded from the assignment results to the intervention.",
    "The study process is presented in Figure 1."
  ]
}